          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Code blocks",
            "id": 85827,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Por qué es útil envolver condicionales dentro de funciones?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Nos ayuda a organizar y reutilizar nuestro código</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">No es así, es lo mismo que reescribir una declaración <code>if</code> cada vez que la necesitamos</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Nos ayuda a organizar y reutilizar nuestro código.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Multiple instructions",
            "id": 85828,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Qué declaración de visualización se ejecuta al llamar a <code>isLying(false)</code>?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"isLying\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"boolean\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome to the Lie Detector 3000&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (boolean === \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;He's lying&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"isLying(\" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Welcome to the Lie Detector 3000\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"He's lying\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Ambas declaraciones de visualización se ejecutan</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Solo se ejecuta la segunda declaración de display</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Ambas declaraciones de visualización se ejecutan.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: One Indent",
            "id": 85830,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Anida la declaración <code>if</code> dentro de la función.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"hasPassed\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"score\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (score &gt;= \" /><text value=\"50\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Passed&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"hasPassed(\" /><text value=\"80\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"27\" /><option startIndex=\"46\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"74\" endIndex=\"75\" /><option startIndex=\"76\" endIndex=\"77\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"(\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\")\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>{</code> seguido de <code>{</code> y luego <code>}</code>, <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Braces and spaces",
            "id": 85831,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Muestra solo <code>\"Checking Score\"</code> en la consola colocándolo fuera de la declaración <code>if</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"hasFailed\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"score\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Checking Score&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (score &lt;= \" /><text value=\"50\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Failed&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"hasFailed(\" /><text value=\"80\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"41\" endIndex=\"57\" /><option startIndex=\"94\" endIndex=\"102\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Checking Score\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"Checking Score\"</code> seguido de <code>\"Failed\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Indenting the entire block",
            "id": 85832,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Muestra ambos mensajes en la consola.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"isLying\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"boolean\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (boolean === \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;He's not lying&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Done&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"isLying(\" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"122\" endIndex=\"126\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"false\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"He's not lying\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Done\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>true</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Code blocks",
            "id": 85833,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Aumenta <code>salary</code> en 500 si es menor que 2100. Muestra <code>salary</code> al final de la función.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"displaySalary\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"salary\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (salary &lt; \" /><text value=\"2100\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  salary = salary + \" /><text value=\"500\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(salary);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"displaySalary(\" /><text value=\"2000\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"79\" /><option startIndex=\"84\" endIndex=\"104\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"2500\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>salary = salary + 500;</code> seguido de <code>console.log(salary);</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
